(taken from)

(20:54:46) (ruler) most things in swing are double buffered
(20:54:49) (ruler) bc swing is so slow

SWT is more along the lines of AWT.

Swing is a beast of an api, alot of the developers that use it dont fully understand it, but swing is INCREDIBLY powerful - which is why it also takes work to understand.[/quote]Sean has spoken.
